                <section class="comment-body font-light"><p>Why doesn't Sonarworks just bump the master volume to the max on install? Is this an Apple limitation?</p>
<p>I bet many users never find this help article and just put up with the low volume, so it might be helpful to add this tip to the install process.</p></section>
