                <section class="comment-body font-light"><p>None of these solutions worked for me.<br>Fortunately I was able to solve it by editing this settings file and changing the volume entries to 1.</p>
<p>/Users/{your username}/Library/Sonarworks/Reference 4/Systemwide/SonarworksSystemwide.settings<br><br>Hopefully it's useful for you while it's not solved.</p>
<p> </p>
<p>UPDATE:<br>Checking the "Adjust output device gain" under Reference 4 settings, solved it.</p></section>
